<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1471] StatsComponent does not calculate number missing for facets</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1471</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The StatsComponent always returns a missing value of 0 for stats.facet. The number of missing is calculated for the overall field statistics, but not for the facets.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12436770">SOLR-1471</key>
            <summary>StatsComponent does not calculate number missing for facets</summary>
